		measure 'Avg Heart Rate over Selected Period' = ```
				
				VAR MaxDate =
				IF(
				    ISFILTERED(dimDate),
				    MAX(dimDate[Date]),
				    [Today]
				)
				VAR Result = 
				    CALCULATE(
				        AVERAGE(fctFitnessStats[Heart Rate]),
				        REMOVEFILTERS(dimDate),
				        DATESBETWEEN(dimDate[Date],MaxDate-[Calculation Period]-1,MaxDate)
				    )
				RETURN
				Result
				```
